                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18351026-2201-offence-1 t18351026-cd-72"></join>21st of August</rs>, 1 painting, value 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18351026-name-492" type="victimName">
